videos.headline: Diabate takes it by himself for a big Michigan jam
videos.description: Moussa Diabate grabs a rebound, then takes it up the court himself for a dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (This slam dunk from Moussa Diabate was too nice) 2022/03/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Frankie Collins spins and scores a tough layup
videos.description: Frankie Collins maneuvers inside and gets a layup to fall for Michigan.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Frankie Collins drops in smooth lay-in) 2022/03/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hunter Dickinson T'd up after voicing frustration to refs
videos.description: Hunter Dickinson drops in a hook shot, but receives a technical foul after voicing his frustration on the no foul call.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Hunter Dickinson T'd up after voicing frustration to refs) 2022/03/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Juwan Howard hears the boos during introductions
videos.description: Fans in Indianapolis rain boos down on Juwan Howard ahead of his first game back from suspension against Indiana.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Juwan Howard hears the boos during introductions) 2022/03/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jackson-Davis, Diabate trade big blocks
videos.description: Trayce Jackson-Davis stuffs Caleb Houstan on one end, but Moussa Diabate answers with a denial of his own.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jackson-Davis, Diabate trade big blocks) 2022/03/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trayce Jackson-Davis gets up for the alley-oop
videos.description: Trayce Jackson-Davis gets up for the beautiful slam

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Trayce Jackson-Davis gets up for the beautiful slam) 2022/03/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hunter Dickinson makes beautiful dish for a basket
videos.description: Hunter Dickinson makes a nice pass to set up an Eli Brooks.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Hunter Dickinson makes beautiful dish for a basket) 2022/03/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Galloway's active hands set up Jackson-Davis' slam
videos.description: Indiana forces a turnover, which springs Trayce Jackson-Davis' dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Trayce Jackson-Davis throws down big flush vs. Michigan Wolverines) 2022/03/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trayce Jackson-Davis gets way up for an alley-oop
videos.description: Xavier Johnson lofts one up high to Trayce Jackson-Davis, who stuffs it home for the Hoosiers.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Trayce Jackson-Davis rocks the rim with jam) 2022/03/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Michigan commits costly turnover down the stretch
videos.description: Moussa Diabate's pass is deflected off the hand of Eli Brooks, which costs the Wolverines late in the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Michigan commits costly turnover down the stretch) 2022/03/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Indiana's big second half takes down Michigan
videos.description: Indiana outscores Michigan 46-28 in the second half to deal a heavy blow to the Wolverines' tournament hopes.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlights (Indiana Hoosiers vs. Michigan Wolverines: Full Highlights) 2022/03/10 ESHEET
